I feel water surrounding me. I feel something touching my cheek.
I open an eye and close it again, it's the morning already: I feel the rough tongue of my cat licking my face to wake me up! What a wonderful moment!
<em>When you have a cat, you never feel alone because you never are! &lt;3</em>
